-- Harper Says Confident Europe Has Will, Can Solve Issues
-- B y   G r e g   Q u i n n
-- 2012-08-16T15:21:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-16/harper-says-he-s-confident-europe-has-will-can-solve-issues.html
European leaders are able to solve
the region’s debt crisis, Canadian Prime Minister  Stephen Harper 
said.  “We have every confidence in our European partners, we
believe they have the capacity and the will to take up their own
challenges,” Harper said at a press conference in Ottawa with
German Chancellor Angela Merkel.  “Europe has taken a number of very important steps” and
other steps are still needed, Harper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
